    IPv4 Support for Proxy Mobile IPv6












      This document specifies extensions to the Proxy Mobile IPv6
      protocol for adding IPv4 protocol support. The scope of IPv4
      protocol support is two-fold: 1) enable IPv4 home address mobility
      support to the mobile node, and 2) allow the mobility entities in
      the Proxy Mobile IPv6 domain to exchange signaling messages over
      an IPv4 transport network.
